OL,3,CElectrician turned boxer quits day job
OL,4,Cafter world title fight in Saudi Arabia
OL,6,FAn electrician-turned-boxer from South
OL,7,FYorkshire has given up his day job
OL,8,Fafter a world title fight in Saudi
OL,9,FArabia.
OL,11,FJosh Padley had just finished a day's
OL,12,Fwork installing solar panels in
OL,13,FDoncaster when he got the call he'd
OL,14,Fbeen waiting for.
OL,16,F"I'd just put my tea in the oven that
OL,17,Fnight when I got the dream phone
OL,18,Fcall," he told ITV Calendar.
