OL,3,CElectrician turned boxer quits day job
OL,4,Cafter world title fight in Saudi Arabia
OL,6,FAfter American boxer Floyd Schofield
OL,7,Ffell ill, Yorkshireman Padley was
OL,8,Fasked to fly out to Riyadh in Saudi
OL,9,FArabia to fight for the WBC
OL,10,Flightweight title.
OL,12,FHe said: "Opportunities like that come
OL,13,Fonce in a lifetime. Obviously I was
OL,14,Fkeen to do everything in my power to
OL,15,Fget the opportunity which is what we
OL,16,Fdid.
OL,18,F"We jumped through every hoop we could
OL,19,Fand somehow we pulled it off and next
OL,20,Fthing you know we're in Saudi Arabia."
