OL,3,CElectrician turned boxer quits day job
OL,4,Cafter world title fight in Saudi Arabia
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old stepped in the ring to
OL,7,Ftake on world champion Shakur
OL,8,FStevenson on Saturday, 22 February -
OL,9,Fjust four days after receiving the
OL,10,Finvite.
OL,12,FStevenson, who has held multiple world
OL,13,Fchampionships in three weight classes,
OL,14,Fcame into the fight with 22 wins and
OL,15,Fzero losses.
OL,17,FWith such little time to prepare,
OL,18,FPadley's head trainer said it was a
OL,19,Fchallenge to get ready for the fight.
