OL,3,CElectrician turned boxer quits day job
OL,4,Cafter world title fight in Saudi Arabia
OL,6,FJason Cunningham told ITV Calendar:
OL,7,F"It was just a case of watching a
OL,8,Flittle bit of Shakur the day we got
OL,9,Fthere, trying to come up with some
OL,10,Fkind of a game plan.
OL,12,F"But really it was just in the moment
OL,13,Fhe had to go out there, give it his
OL,14,Fbest shot and see what happened."
OL,16,FDespite not winning the fight, Padley
OL,17,Fsays his life has changed completely
OL,18,Fand he can now give up his day job
OL,19,Fcrawling through roofs to install
OL,20,Fsolar panels.
