OL,3,CElectrician turned boxer quits day job
OL,4,Cafter world title fight in Saudi Arabia
OL,6,FHe added: "Previously I've always gone
OL,7,Fto work all day and then come to the
OL,8,Fgym for an hour or an hour and a half
OL,9,Fin the evening so it's full on. Now
OL,10,FI'll be able to get two sessions in
OL,11,Fand structure my life around boxing.
OL,13,F"Luckily my boss is very
OL,14,Funderstanding. He's over the moon for
OL,15,Fme."
OL,17,FTobias Cain, Padley's former boss at
OL,18,FScarbrook Plumbing & Heating, said:
OL,19,F"You can't say to someone who's done
OL,20,Fsomething like he did last week 'come
OL,21,Fback here'.
